description:
This is a 19 minute workout called 'HIIT Workout - Insane 15 Minute Spin Bike Workout' from the channel AbundantYou with Dr Kevin.
The workout falls under Cardio/HIIT and Cardio/Indoor biking.
It's suitable for Beginner and Intermediate fitness levels.
You'll need Exercise Bike for this workout.
The workout has a The Firestarter and The Endorphin Wave vibe.
The technique difficulty is Beginner.
The effort required is Moderate.

Original workout description: Try this insane 15 minute spin bike workout today! 

You don't have to spend countless hours busting your butt and sweating buckets to obtain benefits like weight loss, muscle growth, and improved overall health and well-being.

15 Minute Spin Bike HIIT workouts like this one save you time without sacrificing any fitness benefits! 

#HIITWorkout #SpinBikeWorkout #BikeWorkout...
